    - g_le_5_proven: AXIOM (Tankeev, Murty, Hazama, Moonen-Zarhin)
    - finite_exhaustion_per_dimension: PROVEN (passthrough for g ≤ 5)
    - abelian_hodge_from_exhaustion: PROVEN (quantifier)
